**Hookdeck's Streamlined Approach:** Hookdeck supports numerous methods of source authentication.
When you provide your webhook secret during connection setup, Hookdeck **automatically verifies Shopify's signatures** before forwarding events.
Your application only needs to verify Hookdeck's own signature using its standardized approach, which works identically across all supported webhook platforms.
This reduces implementation complexity while improving security consistency.
